CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 9, 1954, pg. 17, reads: "Ex-Legislators - Judge Homer S. Brown whom Jones followed to the Assembly joins well-wishers. Mr Jones must now resign from Legislature. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Man shaking hands with Paul F. Jones, in Pittsburgh City Council Chambers
